Prometheus-grafana install
1.launch a instance for Prometheus(monitor)
2.install git in the instance
3.next install Prometheus.sh file
4.run the script
5.allocate a port number for this Prometheus in security group
6.the check whether its running in that port
Installation history
1  sudo apt update
    2  sudo apt install git -y
    3  git clone https://github.com/yasminjeelani/Prometheus_Grafana.git
    4  cd Prometheus_Grafana
    5  ls
    6  ./install-prometheus.sh
    7  sudo -i
    8  sudo systemctl restart prometheus
    9  sudo systemctl status prometheus
   10  cd ...
   11  cd
   12  cd Prometheus_Grafana
   13  ls
   14  ./ install-grafana.sh 
   15  ./install-grafana.sh 
   16  history

1  vi node-exporter.sh
    2  sudo apt update
    3  sudo apt install git -y
    4  git clone https://github.com/yasminjeelani/Prometheus_Grafana.git
    5  ls
    6  cd Prometheus_Grafana
    7  ls
    8  ./install-node-exporter.sh
    9  history

Install node exporter
1.create a instance for node exporter
2.git clone and run node-exporter.sh file
3. allocate a port for the node
4.check whether port is running
Grafana
1.install grafana in the same instance Prometheus running
2.runn grafana.sh file
3. allocate the port number for grafana and node here.
4. open the port and check
Now the grafana is running in the port

